{"tid":1931524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"報道指金融機構高層要求英國關閉股市兩星期","createTime":"2020-03-18T08:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T08:50:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"47a89e7e0fffb52b2af844ed11f7415780fd61d1","tid":1931524,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1515268_1_L_20200318154615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1515268_1_L_20200318154615.jpg&h=8ca54c01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外電指，有金融機構高級管理層要求英國當局關閉股票市場兩星期。<br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報引述消息人士透露，幾名金融機構高管，包括貝萊德、摩根大通、紐約梅隆銀行等，在日前與英倫銀行新行長貝利(Andrew Bailey)的電話會議上，提出關閉市場的可能性，會中亦討論市場與金融服務行業情況等廣泛議題，不過報道指，與會者都不認為關閉市場有助解決現時危機。<br />\n<br />\n受到新型肺炎疫情影響，全球股市顯著下跌。"},{"pid":"8b8438612ee33362b7ba5368293fb62c2063c5a8","tid":1931524,"uid":173207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"如果唔閂 係咪會跌到阿媽都唔認得"},{"pid":"17814f0b7502d179c5cbc45ae151c554cb77c9a1","tid":1931524,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8b8438612ee33362b7ba5368293fb62c2063c5a8","tid":1931524,"uid":173207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"如果唔閂 係咪會跌到阿媽都唔認得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"復市嗰日肯定精彩"},{"pid":"d74ddf52430e189295504484cf5a1a2448198d8e","tid":1931524,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"17814f0b7502d179c5cbc45ae151c554cb77c9a1","tid":1931524,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8b8438612ee33362b7ba5368293fb62c2063c5a8","tid":1931524,"uid":173207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"如果唔閂 係咪會跌到阿媽都唔認得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"復市嗰日肯定精彩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"停到無事為止。"},{"pid":"3791ed9e9cef102a7ecb8a37f91568bab67